@startuml
actor User
participant ":InternTrackr" as IT
participant ":Parser" as P
participant ":XYZCommandParser" as XCP

User -> IT : run(fullCommand)
IT -> P : parse(fullCommand)

note right of P
  Rejects blank input and
  input containing "|"
end note

alt command needs argument parsing (add, delete, archive, ...)
    P -> XCP : parse(arguments)
    XCP --> P : command
else simple command (list, list archive, overview, ...)
    note right of P : Command created directly
end

P --> IT : command

note right of P
  Diagram simplified.
  Each command routes to its
  own XYZCommandParser class.
end note
@enduml
